+        // [SCENARIO 569462] Verify "Use Emissions In Purch. Doc.", "Item Emissions", "Resource Emissions", "Work/Machine Center Emissions" must be enabled in Sustainability Setup.
+        // When "Enable Value Chain Tracking" is enabled.
